_sText:
The most epic froot based collab now actually finished and not broken!

Now with 1 new stage, 2 new bonuses, a detailed hub, a stage re-order, nasty bits removed, new and fixed eastereggs and heaps of other stuff!
  • Tier 5, starting from Tier 1!
  • 21 stages!
  • 7 bonuses!
  • Eastereggs galore including 3 secret surfs!
  • 10 pre-made stripper relays to tweak the map!
Map requires bhop for multiple stages and a model collision fix plugin for the Burger King bonus (B4) cause it took up 60% limits and I didn't properly fix it here.

Map is marked NSFW due to use of suggestive images & comedic non-pornographic cartoon penises, same as the "original" version on here.

This was supposed to be released on Jan 1st 2019, sorry to everyone I let down. It took a lot of pain working though my disability, but it's finally here for real. Thank you to everyone who held the space in voice chats or on Twitch, I would not be able to finish it without all of you.

CS:GO port by granis: https://gamebanana.com/mods/414675
TF2 port coming someday.

Showcase video by Dini, thank you!
